		<title>05INDUSTRY:PADIHAM LANCS.</title>
		<content>{                                      
{MULLARDS:}Television tube makers.     
  Mullards is part of Philips          
 Electronics, Holland.The components   
 made here are delivered to Durham,    
 where the completed tube is assembled.
                                       
 1.65 million tubes are made each year 
 and 5 out of every 6 Japaanese firms  
 use Mullard tubes. They also make the 
 videodiscs used to store the DOMESDAY 
 information.                          
                                       
 1100 people are employed in 2         
 factories.The glass factory works     
 continously,24 hours a day,7 days a   
 week.The furnace has 5-6 year life.   
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
